	   <tr><td colspan=2>well, i dont nuke in groups, i use the stun spells. whichever seems approite at the time, stun (for monsters on the chanter), holy might (for aggo creatues  like sarnaks and orcs), or even tremor (for cactus men and rinos). just my thought. sides, stuns can actually save u from healing too much =). have fun all<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
