	   <tr><td colspan=2>Got to completely agree with you, Clerics can do alot more than med and heal.  <br><br>With stuns, most Tanks see them as Blasting, we can save alot of damage.  With fear and a snarer we can let the group kill alot more with little loss in hit points.  Root will save your rear end if you don't have snare.<br><br>Ok you died because your Cleric was OOM it happens.  But did you listen or even ask him his mana before you pulled?  Did he tell you he was going to nuke a bit to get his Evocation skill up?  Did you ask him in a tell not to nuke so much and save his mana?  There are new Clerics out there who need to learn their roll a bit better, as there are also Tanks who ignore the Cleric's mana reports and pull anyway.<br><br>Sounds like a low level new Cleric and a low level new group screwed up.  As I said ghet over it, learn from it, but don't assume Cleric's can't ever blast.  Remember that the Cleric can solo better that a Warrior at almost any level using root and nuke, so maybe our blasts are worth something.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
